source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT [CANTIDAD]
      ,[IUC]
      ,[NUMERO DE CEDULA] AS NumeroDeCedula
      ,[CLIENTE]
      ,[NUEVO EJECUTIVO] AS NuevoEjecutivo
  FROM [dbo].[BI_IUCMetasFinanciero]

SELECT [Ptr_Id]
      ,[Ptr_PK_Cedula]
      ,[Ptr_NumPatrono]
      ,[Ptr_Nombre]
      ,[Ptr_Direccion]
      ,[Ptr_Telefono]
      ,[Ptr_CodDistrito]
  FROM dbo.[BI_PatronosSIC]
  WHERE [Ptr_Id] BETWEEN  1 AND 25
